            <title>[FLINK-3450] RocksDB Backed Window Fails with KryoSerializer</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-3450</link>
                <project id="12315522" key="FLINK">Flink</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;It fails due to concurrent use of the KryoSerializer when asynchronously serializing the &lt;tt&gt;StateDescriptor&lt;/tt&gt; during checkpointing.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
